{"word":"H2106 - זָוִית - zâvîyth - zaw-veeth' - Corner","slug":"H2106","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">זָוִית</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>zâvîyth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>zaw-veeth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Corner"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D6;&#x05D5;&#x05D9;&#x05EA; - za&#x0302;v&#x0131;&#x0302;yth</b> - <i>zaw-veeth'</i><p/>Apparently from the same root as <a href=\"#/H2099\">H2099</a> (in the sense of <i>prominence</i>); an <i>angle</i> (as <i>projecting</i>), that is, (by implication) a <i>corner column</i> (or <i>anta</i>): - corner (stone)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4200\">H4200</a>"}]}